The Year Of The Horse is the name of a VHS released by singer/songwriter Sinéad O'Connor in 1991. The concert was recorded live at Forest National, Brussels (Belgium), on 29 October 1990 and Ahoy Sport Paleis, Rotterdam (Netherlands), on 30 October 1990. The concert was re-released in 2004 in DVD format as Live: The Year of the Horse/The Value of Ignorance.